headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Boosted Production Speeds Across Your Businesses
content:
Executives will receive 2X Special Cargo Crates from Special Cargo Warehouse manager Lupe, while Production Speeds for all Biker Businesses, Bunker Stock, and Nightclub Warehouse Stock are also all doubled.

To help maximize the benefits from your Criminal Enterprises, Upgrades and Modifications for the Executive Office, Bunker, Nightclub, and Biker Clubhouse are all 40% off.
